{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"01177dafd6","title":"关于精兵简政问题给谢觉截、陈正人“的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"63023eb36e","index":0,"year":1942,"month":8,"day":19,"articleId":"01177dafd6"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji17","name":"毛泽东全集第17卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji17.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji17":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"51de071178","type":"paragraph","text":"关于精兵简政问题给谢觉截、陈正人“的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"01177dafd6"},{"id":"5fe1af58d4","type":"paragraph","text":"（1942年8月19日）觉载、正人二同志今天所谈二届参议会应以准备精兵简政为中心，在开会以前应实行精简，开会以后应检查（点验）精简，而精简包括精少、效能、统一诸方面。今看本日（十九日）报纸《精兵简政在晋翼鲁豫边区》一文，所包事项尤多，尚有节省、反官像主义诸项，此文我看很好，请你们也看一看，是否我们这里可以完全仿效？此事应在整风学习完后来一个如像整风这样的大举，方能普遍、深入与切实见效，过去还只是耳边风敬礼！","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"01177dafd6"},{"id":"f0657d33a6","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"01177dafd6"},{"id":"626c37a131","type":"paragraph","text":"八月十九日D陈正人（1907-1972），江西遂川人，当时任中共中央西北局组织部","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"01177dafd6"}],"page":{"id":"446bdb6426","publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"01177dafd6","start":121,"end":121}}}},"__N_SSG":true}